    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-08-03T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-08-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="370"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d370">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Dun</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-08-03">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 3, 1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Our minister to China was promptly instructed to exercise good offices for Japan,
                    as requested, and he has informed the Department that he is doing so.</p>
            </div>
